\u003eNew thoughts:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eI still enjoyed it. Twilight is like comfort food for me. It's not deep; it's something you definitely don't want to analyze.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1418709115ra/12881047.gif\" class=\"escapedImg\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eYep, if I think too m\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003cspan id=\"freeText12377792597667168060\" style=\"display:none\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFirst Read: Several years ago\u003cbr\u003eSecond Read: December 2014 \u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1399843196ra/9601813.gif\" class=\"escapedImg\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWay back when, I used to make fun of Twilight, but one night I was bored and decided to watch it. \u003cem\u003eI *liked* it.\u003c/em\u003e So then, I binge read all the books and watched all the movies (and bought them all too). But it's been a couple years. So, I'm going back in to see if anything has changed.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNew thoughts:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eI still enjoyed it. Twilight is like comfort food for me. It's not deep; it's something you definitely don't want to analyze.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1418709115ra/12881047.gif\" class=\"escapedImg\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eYep, if I think too much about it, that definitely doesn't make sense.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1418709115ra/12881048.gif\" class=\"escapedImg\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eYep, I get it. But it's not about that for me. It's just a simple fantasy romance that happens to focus on *vampires.* I've always been a vampire fan, don't ask me why. I guess I can blame it on Anne Rice? \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eAnyway, I never expected Bella to be a kick-ass heroine and Edward never seemed like a stalker to me. I didn't \"read\" that much into it. There was just always something about Bella that I could identify with and relate to. I just think for what it is, it's a great story. :D\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1418608996ra/12845557.gif\" class=\"escapedImg\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003ca data-text-id=\"12377792597667168060\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent($(this));; return false;\"\u003e...more\u003c/a\u003e\n\n          \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"reviewFooter uitext buttons\"\u003e\n        \n\n\u003ctr class=\"no_border feedFooterReview\" id=\"update_comment_stuff_Review759079607\"\u003e\n  \u003ctd colspan=\"2\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"updateActionLinks\"\u003e\n        \u003ca class=\"right flag\" rel=\"nofollow\" id=\"flag_link759079607\" title=\"Flag this review as inappropriate.\" href=\"/flagged/new?resource_id=759079607\u0026amp;resource_type=Review\u0026amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F41865.Twilight\"\u003eflag\u003c/a\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n      \u003cspan class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_review_759079607'\u003e\u003ca id=\"like_count_review_759079607\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"/rating/voters/759079607?resource_type=Review\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"likesCount\"\u003e44 likes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u003ca rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"jsLike like_it gr-button gr-button--small\" href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true\u0026amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Freviews%2F41865\"\u003eLike\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"/review/show/759079607?book_show_action=false\u0026amp;from_review_page=2\"\u003esee review\u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n    \u003cdiv id='comments_for_review_759079607' style='display: none;'\u003e\n\u003cdiv class='brown_comment'\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"loadingLinkSpan\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"loadingLink\" data-remote=\